    "markdown": "# Willkommen {#index .unnumbered}\n\n\n\n\n\nEine Einführung in R für Mitarbeitende am BIBB.\n\n\n::: {.cell layout-align=\"center\"}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](./pic/00_frontpage.png){fig-align='center' width=70% height=70%}\n:::\n:::\n\n\nHier entsteht das Begleitskript für die R-Kurse am BIBB 29.-30.09. und 06.-07.10.2022\nMelden Sie sich gerne bei Fragen oder Wünschen unter andreas.filser[at]uol.de\n\n<!-- :::{.callout-note} -->\n<!-- Note that there are five types of callouts, including:  -->\n<!-- `note`, `tip`, `warning`, `caution`, and `important`. -->\n<!-- ::: -->\n\n**Kurszeiten**\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n`````{=html}\n<table class=\" lightable-material table table-striped table-hover table-condensed\" style=\"font-family: Roboto; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: auto !important; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th style=\"text-align:left;font-weight: bold;color: white !important;font-size: 0px;\"> Tag </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:left;font-weight: bold;color: white !important;font-size: 0px;\"> Start </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:left;font-weight: bold;color: white !important;font-size: 0px;\"> Ende </th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n<tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> 29.09.2022 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> 08:30 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> 15:15 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> 30.09.2022 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> 08:30 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> 15:30 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> 06.10.2022 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> 08:30 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> 15:30 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> 07.10.2022 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> 08:30 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:left;\"> 15:30 </td>\n  </tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n`````\n:::\n:::\n",
